    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由曾打造《精灵与森林》与《精灵与萤火意志》的获奖工作室 Moon Studios 倾力呈现，《恶意不息》是一款风格独特、直击感官的动作角色扮演游戏。游戏设定于一个精心构建的世界之中，主打硬核的类魂战斗体验。在这里，每一击都至关重要，好友亦可随时加入战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持单人游玩或最多四名玩家在线合作畅玩。直面凶残的敌人，建造属于自己的家园，在一个被瘟疫、贪婪与荣耀撕裂的世界中，亲手开辟属于你的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/66ad635e0cbc6dc24f1b5082322ff9bf.poster.avif?t=1769237814\" width=1146 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/66ad635e0cbc6dc24f1b5082322ff9bf.webm?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/66ad635e0cbc6dc24f1b5082322ff9bf.mp4?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精准且打击感十足的<strong>战斗</strong>体验，每一次交锋都至关重要。现加入多种难度选项，方便你根据个人玩法风格灵活调整体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 海量<strong>战利品</strong>等你发现：通过收集武器、盔甲及符文，打造属于你的独特角色。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 跌宕起伏的主线<strong>剧情</strong>，带你领略一个精心构建的独特世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一座随时间演变的<strong>鲜活岛屿</strong>：新的事件、商贩和挑战接连登场。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>房屋建造</strong>与制作系统直接融入核心玩法。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在线合作畅玩</strong>，无需切换独立模式，无冗余设计。只有完整的游戏体验，与好友共享。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>无微交易</strong>，一切皆可通过游玩获得。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/96f7af36a9178725e4ac7b57c58a3a8f.webp?t=1769237814\" width=600 height=60 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在主线剧情的<strong>在线合作模式</strong>中，与最多三名好友共享你的世界与进度。圣地岛的每一个任务、每一名首领、以及每一寸土地，都可以与好友共享，也可按自己的节奏独自探索。是结交盟友、选择背叛，还是独自精进，全由你决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/c39b35281aa2a0a37526a07b742506f4.poster.avif?t=1769237814\" width=1146 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/c39b35281aa2a0a37526a07b742506f4.webm?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/c39b35281aa2a0a37526a07b742506f4.mp4?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/fd8360af891ce2afb01b3d32dec82c3c.avif?t=1769237814\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/72c94fc2334b717c503ffc0e211f2a0c.webp?t=1769237814\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在强调策略与出手时机的类魂战斗系统中磨练你的战斗技能。在令人心跳加速的交锋中，对抗骇人的怪物、敌军士兵与极具挑战性的首领。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过每种武器独特的动作招式，切身感受武器的重量与速度。为武器附魔、打造稀有盔甲，并构建契合你玩法风格的专属配装。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选择你的国度等级：</strong>通过多种<strong>难度选项</strong>，你可以根据个人喜好随心定制这段旅程，无论是专注剧情推进，还是追求完整而硬核的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/7682daaafd53f92ecfbe06d0ad9f99e9.poster.avif?t=1769237814\" width=1146 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/7682daaafd53f92ecfbe06d0ad9f99e9.webm?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/7682daaafd53f92ecfbe06d0ad9f99e9.mp4?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/46ead50b8cf4dd131b88b4b1a853a3e9.webp?t=1769237814\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索过程中采集木材、矿石与食物；制作能够恢复生命值并提升属性值的料理；并前往圣城，在那里你可以购买房产、升级装备，并存放你的战利品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/a90a557581d370c7d8d8de8bb61aa8ff.poster.avif?t=1769237814\" width=1146 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/a90a557581d370c7d8d8de8bb61aa8ff.webm?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/a90a557581d370c7d8d8de8bb61aa8ff.mp4?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/883d6f6b58b204c3e219adbfa22ab9bb.webp?t=1769237814\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >|时间来到<strong>天之拥841年</strong>。哈罗尔国王已然驾崩，而那场千年未现的邪祟瘟疫“灾疠”，再次降临世间。<br><br>你是一名<strong>塞利姆</strong>，一位神秘的圣战士，发誓不惜一切代价根除瘟疫。然而，当叛乱、信仰与腐败在圣地岛上交织碰撞，你所踏足的每一片森林、每一处地牢，都可能暗藏新的挑战与变数。每个地点都经过精心构建，隐藏的秘密与宝藏散落其中，往往潜藏在最意想不到的角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/a4ac2757024414ea105dc0d29ef6b90b.poster.avif?t=1769237814\" width=1146 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/a4ac2757024414ea105dc0d29ef6b90b.webm?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/a4ac2757024414ea105dc0d29ef6b90b.mp4?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/7e4f6242294c3ef12cdad4172753d864.webp?t=1769237814\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><br><strong> </strong><br>在圣城这座宏大的主城中稍作休整，在这里，你可以购置房产、挑选家具并随心装饰，亲手打造独属于你的家园。在岸边垂钓，于田间耕耘、收获食材，烹饪能够恢复生命值并提升属性值的料理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识形形色色的商贩与城镇居民，让圣城重现往日的辉煌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/fe4ee54c2013c2b74337209ae7b6b1f4.poster.avif?t=1769237814\" width=1146 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/fe4ee54c2013c2b74337209ae7b6b1f4.webm?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/fe4ee54c2013c2b74337209ae7b6b1f4.mp4?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/19718c3bb3d797fc1be7f7a3fba048aa.webp?t=1769237814\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《恶意不息》中，圣地岛的每一寸土地、你遇到的每一个生灵，乃至每一帧动画，皆为人工匠心打造，倾注了对细节的极致追求。感受昼夜更替间的天气流转与光影变幻，细听微风拂过叶丛的呢喃；在投身下一场惊心动魄的战斗挑战前，不妨驻足片刻，尽情领略这如画的壮丽景致。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/2f31af84f101e03d6d389672a435af20.poster.avif?t=1769237814\" width=1146 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/2f31af84f101e03d6d389672a435af20.webm?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/2f31af84f101e03d6d389672a435af20.mp4?t=1769237814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371980/extras/48951adc952ef6f77416d1de4ed298b7.webp?t=1769237814\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《恶意不息》<strong>不含微交易</strong>、不设捷径、不存在付费取胜，只有纯粹而扎实的游戏体验。<strong></strong><br><br><br><br><br> </p>",
